      <title>0x0002.Hugo添加不蒜子计数器指南</title>
      <link>/posts/0x0002.hugo%E6%B7%BB%E5%8A%A0%E4%B8%8D%E8%92%9C%E5%AD%90%E8%AE%A1%E6%95%B0%E5%99%A8%E6%8C%87%E5%8D%97/</link>
